import React, { useEffect, useState } from 'react' const Question = ({question,onChange,setQuestions,questions}) => { const [answer,setAnswer] = useState(""); useEffect(()=>{ setAnswer(question?.answer) },[question]) const onSave = (sequenceNum)=>{ setQuestions(questions.map( question=>question.sequenceNum===sequenceNum?{...question,answer}:question )) console.log(questions) } const onReset =(sequenceNum)=>{ setQuestions(questions.map( question=>question.sequenceNum===sequenceNum?{...question,answer:""}:question )) setAnswer(""); } return (
Question Type : {question.questionType}
Question No. {question.sequenceNum}

{question.questionDetails}
